    "en": {
      "title": "Mobile fuel dispenser to distribute fuel for three wheelers and generators",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Power and Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekera yesterday said mobile fuel dispensers will be used as a pilot project to provide fuel for three wheelers and generators.",
        "Taking to Twitter, Minister Wijesekera said the dispensers will be used in large open spaces away from the fuel stations.",
        "The measure is expected to provide fuel to three wheelers, delivery bikes and cans. The Minister said he hopes to implement the system across the island promptly."
      ],
